				<h1 class="entry-title">The Healthy Sex Talk: Teaching Kids Consent, Ages 1-21</h1>
		
		<div class="post-info"><span class="date published time" title="2013-03-20T14:00:08+00:00">March 20, 2013</span>  By <span class="author vcard"><span class="fn"><a href="http://goodmenproject.com/author/the-editors/" class="fn n" title="the Editors" rel="author">the Editors</a></span></span> <span class="post-comments"><a href="http://goodmenproject.com/families/the-healthy-sex-talk-teaching-kids-consent-ages-1-21/#comments">86 Comments</a></span> </div>		<div class="entry-content">
			<div id="tweetbutton91043" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fgoodmenproject.com%2Ffamilies%2Fthe-healthy-sex-talk-teaching-kids-consent-ages-1-21%2F&amp;via=goodmenproject&amp;text=The%20Healthy%20Sex%20Talk%3A%20Teaching%20Kids%20Consent%2C%20Ages%201-21&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fgoodmenproject.com%2Ffamilies%2Fthe-healthy-sex-talk-teaching-kids-consent-ages-1-21%2F" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://twitter.com']);" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://goodmenproject.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div>
