		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>My fear about that &#8220;bathing suit area&#8221; thing is the shame that can come with self-touch and also eventually with partner touch. </p>
<p>I&#8217;m not sure there is one 100% good term to use, but for parents to be having these conversations regularly with their children is probably what will do the best to empower a child to speak up if they&#8217;ve been victimized.</p>
